        About this item

        • The TCL 40XL works with most major U.S. carriers, including Verizon, AT&T and T-Mobile. This android phone is also compatible with Tracfone, Simple Mobile, Cricket, Ultra Mobile, Pure talk, H2O, Tello, Google Fi, Jethro Mobile, Lycamobile, Mint Mobile, MetroPCS, Ting, US Mobile, Family Mobile, etc. This cell phone isn't compatible with Visible, Boost Mobile, Boost Infinite, Assurance Wireless, Consumer Cellular, Sprint, Air Voice, Pine Cellular, Union Wireless, Xfinity, etc.
        • 6.75-inch large screen cell phone - The TCL 40XL cellphone, featuring a 6.75-inch screen with a 20:9 aspect ratio and dual stereo speakers, lets you enjoy the feel of a movie.
        • 128GB of storage for everything important - The TCL 40XL smartphone 128GB offers ample storage for your apps, photos, and videos, you won't run out of space, and you can add even more space with a microSD card of up to 512GB.
        • Take it to the next level - This unlocked smartphone combines a MediaTek Helio processor with 4GB of RAM and the Android 13 operating system for fast and efficient performance. 4GB of RAM allows you to run multiple apps at once.
        • Triple camera with 50MP AI - TCL smartphone with triple 50Mpx AI camera allows you to deliver superb high-resolution images in all lighting conditions, with spectacular results, especially in low light. With TCL 40XL, you can capture the great moments of your life.
        • 5000mAh Long Life Battery - This cell phone equipped with 5000mAh battery relieves you from battery anxiety and supports multiple business tasks and fun moments all day long.Smart charging mode slows down battery aging.
        • PLEASE NOTE - TCL 40XL mobile phone does not support 5G network and NFC. This Model comes with a one-year limited US manufacturer warranty, single sim and Nano size sim card only.

            Product Description

            TCL 40XL is a US version phone. If you plan to use it outside the U.S., please provide the following band information and confirm network compatibility with your local carrier.

            Band:

            2G-GSM:850/900/1800/1900,

            3G-WCDMA:B2/B4/B5,

            4G-FDD LTE:B2/B4/B5/B12/B13/B25/B26/B66/B71,

            4G-TDD LTE:B41(HPUE)


            Compatible with major carriers

            Verizon, AT&T and T-Mobile. This android phone is also compatible with Tracfone, Simple Mobile, Cricket, Ultra Mobile, Pure talk, H2O, Tello, Google Fi, Jethro Mobile, Lycamobile, Mint Mobile, MetroPCS, Ting, US Mobile, Family Mobile, etc


            Not support carriers

            Boost Mobile, Consumer Cellular ATT, Visible, Boost Infinite, Assurance Wireless, Sprint, Air Voice, Pine Cellular, Union Wireless, Xfinity, etc.


            Wi-Fi calling support on these carriers

            T-Mobile, Ultra Mobile, Google Fi, Lycamobile, Mint Mobile, Simple Mobile, Tello, Ting, Family Mobile, MetroPCS, Pure talk, H2O, Republic


            General information:

            OS: Android 13

            Dimensions: 167.91mm * 76.5mm * 8.79mm

            Main LCD Size: 6.75 inch


            Memory：

            RAM: 4GB

            ROM: 128GB

            External storage: Micro SD, up to 512GB


            Available Ports:

            SIM Slot: 4FF (Nano-SIM)

            TF card slot: Y

            eSIM: N

            Audio Jack: 3.5mm audio jack


            Camera:

            Rear camera: 50M + 2 M + 2M

            Front camera: 8M


            Battery:

            Typical Capacity: 5000 (mAh)

            Charging Technology: 9V2A


            System Language:

            English, Chinese, Korean, Polish, Portuguese, German, Vietnamese, Spanish and French

            What's in the box

          • 1 x TCL 40XL Cell Phone
          • 1 x 18W Charger (9V 2A)
